        "languageCode": "fr",
        "value": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ffffff\" size=\"5\"><u><b>Datatable</b></u></font></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ffffff\" size=\"5\"><u><b><br></b></u></font></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#ffffff\">Le Data Table est un composant puissant conçu pour afficher et manipuler des données tabulaires de manière interactive.&nbsp;</font></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#ffffff\">Il combine la flexibilité d'une table de données avec l'esthétique d'une carte. Ce composant offre des fonctionnalités essentielles telles que la pagination, le tri des colonnes, le filtrage et l'édition des données. Il prend en charge différentes sources de données (API REST, données locales) et gère intelligemment les clés étrangères.</font></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font color=\"#ffffff\">Sa configuration flexible permet une personnalisation poussée de l'affichage (colonnes, formats, styles) tout en maintenant une expérience utilisateur cohérente et intuitive.&nbsp;</font></p>"
      },
      {
        "languageCode": "en",
        "value": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; background-color: rgb(31, 41, 55);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#ffffff\">The Data Table is a powerful component designed to display and interactively manipulate tabular data.</font></span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 13px;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" color=\"#ffffff\" style=\"background-color: rgb(31, 41, 55);\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures;\"></span><br></font></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; background-color: rgb(31, 41, 55);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" color=\"#ffffff\">It combines the flexibility of a data table with the aesthetics of a card. This component offers essential features such as pagination, column sorting, filtering, and data editing. It supports various data sources (REST API, local data) and intelligently manages foreign keys.</font></span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; min-height: 13px;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" color=\"#ffffff\" style=\"background-color: rgb(31, 41, 55);\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures;\"></span><br></font></p><p class=\"p3\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; background-color: rgb(31, 41, 55);\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\" style=\"\" color=\"#ffffff\">Its flexible configuration allows for extensive customization of the display (columns, formats, styles) while maintaining a consistent and intuitive user experience.</font></span></p>"
